JF  - Academy of Management Review
JO  - AMR
SP  - 647
EP  - 676
VL  - 17
IS  - 4
PB  - Academy of Management
N2  - Research on organizational punishment has focused on the effects of punishment on the disciplined subordinate. This article invokes a justice perspective to develop a framework for studying the effects of punishment on observers?other organizational members who take an interest in a particular punishment event. Research propositions are offered as a guide to future investigations, and implications for management are discussed.
AB  - Research on organizational punishment has focused on the effects of punishment on the disciplined subordinate. This article invokes a justice perspective to develop a framework for studying the effects of punishment on observers?other organizational members who take an interest in a particular punishment event. Research propositions are offered as a guide to future investigations, and implications for management are discussed.
